Requirement.ObjectText:
[F: APA_HMI]Searching Abort - Park In
The APA function shall be exited if the following condition occures during searching:

ESP Off condition: WorkingSt_ESP = 0x0: Off;

[F: APA_HMI]Searching Abort - Park Out
The APA function shall be exited if the following condition occures during searching:

ESP Off condition: WorkingSt_ESP = 0x0: Off;

[F: APA_HMI]Guidance Abort - Park In
The APA function shall be exited if the following condition occures during guidance:

ESP Off condition: WorkingSt_ESP = 0x0: Off;
